AMH Conversations is BACK! This time we are there partnering the Ministry of Tourism in support of the upcoming UNWTO. Just a brief background. AMH Conversations was launched by Alpha Media Holdings to provide a platform for thought leadership discussion on all aspects of business across all sectors. Areas for discussion include economic policy, business strategy, markets, technology and many others that are not only informative and interesting but thought provoking and challenging. Alpha Media Holdings in partnership with the Ministry of Tourism will be hosting two AMH Conversations in Harare and Victoria Falls in the build up toward the UNWTO General Assembly in August. The first event which will be hosted in Harare in July and we have lined up the following speakers listed below. The final event will be held in August in Victoria Falls. We will be inviting business leaders, Ambassadors of the respective countries represented in Zimbabwe, General Managers from all the seven hotel partners, Government Ministers and CEOs of the leading tour operators etc.
