We have also invited the 45 Brand Ambassadors selected by the Hon. Minister Eng. Dr Walter Mzembi. NewsDay will give you a live report from tomorrow’s event. Check the advert for our latest ‪#‎AMHconversations‬ event that will see Minister Mzembi and his counterpart Zambian Minister of Tourism Sylvia Masebo will converse in under the theme: UNWTO….can we pull it off?